sailpoint.object

Class ApprovalSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.ApprovalSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class ApprovalSet
extends AbstractXmlObject
    A class used during the approval process.

    This is an object that can be used to examine the items contained in a set. These typically live in the attributes map of an Approval WorkItem.
